# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/CreativeWork
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/CreativeWork> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/CreativeWork> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass> _:genid28 .
_:genid28 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
_:genid28 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#intersectionOf> _:genid30 .
_:genid30 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> _:genid29 .
_:genid29 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#nil> .
_:genid29 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> <http://schema.org/CreativeWork> .
_:genid29 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
_:genid30 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000030> .
_:genid30 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/CreativeWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Resource> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/CreativeWork> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "An information content entity that refers to a manifestation of someone's creative effort."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/CreativeWork> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> "2024-03-22. Sasha Bruns - Unlike schema:CreativeWork, nfdicore:CreativeWork is specialized to cover digital creative works only. Through the mapping to \"schema:CreativeWork and 'information content entity'\", we exclude material creative works such as real paintings, architectural objects, and other physical artifacts, which fall outside the scope of nfdicore:CreativeWork."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/CreativeWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A creative work refers to a digital intellectual or artistic resource, e.g. a dataset, metadata, a guideline, a software and other materials offering relevant information or instructions within their specific domains."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/CreativeWork> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "creative work"@en .
