<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Person> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "An agent that represents a single human individual."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Person> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> "2024-03-24. Sasha Bruns - the class is not mapped to NCBITaxon_9606 (homo sapiens) due to different scope of the ontologies. \"Person\" in nfdicore represents entities with specific roles, responsibilities, and attributes within an organization, and is not limited to its biological characteristics."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A resource that represents a single person."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/2.0.0> .
