# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/ProvidedResource
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/ProvidedResource> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/ProvidedResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#ObsoleteClass> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/ProvidedResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A resource that has been provided by a contributor. The class should be used to distinguisch between a resource from the resources that only have a supportive role in other resources, but have not been an active part of the NFDI4Culture."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/ProvidedResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A resource that identifies a resource provided to the NFDI."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/ProvidedResource> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/2.0.0> .
