# https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Publication
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Publication> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
