<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Publication> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A published scholarly work that reports on ongoing activity about or within a resource, e.g. a dataset."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Publication> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/2.0.0> .
