<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/PublisherRole> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A role inhering in an agent that is realized when the bearer participates in the publishing of the document."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/PublisherRole> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/2.0.0> .
