<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Service> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "An information content entity that refers to offerings provided by individuals or organizations to facilitate and contribute to the specific goals."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Service> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Services are resources offered by organizations or people to support and contribute to the predefined goals of a project. Services may encompass a diverse range of contributions such as data curation, specialized expertise, skill and various other forms of support."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Service> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/2.0.0> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Service> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "service"@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Service> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#example> "Data curation for HeiDATA, Expertise for the development and application of LIDO"@en .
