<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/Specification> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> "2024-03-24. Sasha Bruns: specifications have duel nature - they are both directive information entities guiding actions (plan specification) and digital intellectual resources providing relevant information and guidelines (creative work)."@en .
