<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/TechnologicalMeans> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000104> .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/TechnologicalMeans> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A plan specification that refers to technology employed for the creation, management, utilization, or control of a resource."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/TechnologicalMeans> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A technology, e.g. a web application or a programming framework used in a resource."@en .
<https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/TechnologicalMeans> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/2.0.0> .
